      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Deseed the <strong>yellow pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
