    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the noodles are soaking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced yellow pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p>",
