    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has softened, add the<strong> sliced garlic </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>softened wheat noodles</strong>, reserving 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml] </span><strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
